---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Empirical BBQ | Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Empirical BBQ — how we use local browser storage, anonymous Cloudflare Web Analytics, Amazon Associate affiliate links, and programmatic advertising cookies."
  ogUrl="https://empiricalbbq.com/privacy"
  favicon="🔒"
  bodyClass="page-privacy min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-base-850 text-base-300 font-display antialiased selection:bg-flame-500/30"
  showBanner={false}
>
  <div class="relative z-10 flex-1 w-full">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="pt-14 sm:pt-16 pb-8 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-flame-500/10 ring-1 ring-flame-500/40 px-3.5 py-1.5 mb-6">
          <span class="text-sm">🔒</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-flame-300 uppercase">Legal</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white leading-[1.05]">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-base-500 font-mono">Last updated: July 11, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Policy body -->
      <main class="policy pb-16 space-y-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-base-300">
        <section class="rounded-2xl bg-base-800/60 ring-1 ring-base-700 p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-xl shadow-black/30 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy explains how <strong class="text-white">Empirical BBQ</strong> ("we", "us", or "our"),
            operating the website at <span class="font-mono text-base-200">empiricalbbq.com</span> and its cooking
            calculators, handles information when you use the site. Empirical BBQ is a set of client-side calculators;
            we do <strong class="text-white">not</strong> operate user accounts and do not collect names, email
            addresses, or payment details through this site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">1.</span> Local Browser Storage (localStorage)</h2>
          <p>
            Our calculators save your preferences and inputs directly in your browser using
            <span class="font-mono text-base-200">localStorage</span> — for example, your saved rig configuration,
            wrap and pit selections, weights, and other tool settings ("layout saving"). This data is stored
            <strong class="text-white">only on your device</strong>, is never transmitted to us or to any server, and is
            used solely to remember your setup between visits and across our tools. You can erase it at any time by
            clearing your browser's site data for this domain, or by using any in-app "reset" controls we provide.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">2.</span> Anonymous Usage Analytics (Cloudflare Web Analytics)</h2>
          <p>
            We use <strong class="text-white">Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> to understand aggregate, anonymous usage
            of the site (such as page views and general performance). Cloudflare Web Analytics is privacy-first: it does
            <strong class="text-white">not</strong> use cookies, does not fingerprint individuals, and does not collect
            personally identifiable information or track you across other websites. The statistics we see are aggregated
            and cannot be used to identify you. See
            <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Web Analytics</a>
            for details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">3.</span> Amazon Associate Affiliate Links</h2>
          <p>
            Empirical BBQ is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising
            program. Some outbound links on our pages are affiliate links, and
            <strong class="text-white">as an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases</strong> made through
            them, at no additional cost to you. When you click an affiliate link and visit Amazon, your activity on
            Amazon is governed by
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a>,
            not this policy. We do not receive your personal purchase details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">4.</span> Programmatic Advertising &amp; Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We may display advertising served by third-party programmatic ad networks, including
            <strong class="text-white">Google AdSense</strong>. These networks may use cookies — including Google's
            <strong class="text-white">DART cookie</strong> — to serve interest-based ads based on your visits to this
            and other websites. Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to personalize the ads you see.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">Your consent choice.</strong> On your first visit we show a cookie consent
            banner with <strong class="text-white">Accept</strong> and <strong class="text-white">Reject</strong>
            options. Until you choose, analytics and advertising storage are disabled by default via Google Consent
            Mode. Your choice is saved on your device in <span class="font-mono text-base-200">localStorage</span> under
            the key <span class="font-mono text-base-200">pitmaster_consent</span> (value <span class="font-mono text-base-200">granted</span>
            or <span class="font-mono text-base-200">denied</span>), so the banner does not reappear. To change your
            decision, clear this site's browser storage and reload — the banner will show again.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5 text-base-400">
            <li>
              You can opt out of Google's use of advertising cookies by visiting
              <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.
            </li>
            <li>
              You can opt out of interest-based advertising from many participating vendors at
              <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info</a>
              and
              <a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.eu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Your Online Choices</a> (EU).
            </li>
            <li>
              You may also disable cookies through your browser settings, though some site features that rely on local
              storage may be affected.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">5.</span> Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
          <p>
            We do not require registration and do not collect names, email addresses, passwords, or payment
            information on this site. We do not sell or rent personal information. The only data tied to you personally
            lives in your own browser's local storage, as described in Section 1.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">6.</span> Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our site links to third-party websites (such as Amazon and advertisers). We are not responsible for the
            privacy practices or content of those sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policy of any site you
            visit through our links.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">7.</span> Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            This site is intended for a general audience and is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly
            collect personal information from children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">8.</span> Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes take effect when posted on this page, and the
            "Last updated" date above will be revised accordingly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-flame-400">9.</span> Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this Privacy Policy can be directed to
            <a href="mailto:privacy@empiricalbbq.com">privacy@empiricalbbq.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <p class="text-[13px] text-base-500 pt-2">
          This document is provided for general informational purposes and does not constitute legal advice. Consider
          consulting a qualified professional to confirm compliance with the laws applicable to your jurisdiction.
        </p>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer (matches index chrome + status bar) -->
  <footer class="relative z-10 border-t border-base-700 bg-base-900/70 backdrop-blur">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-xs font-medium text-base-400 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
        <a href="/brisket-calculator" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Brisket Calculator</a>
        <a href="/stall-predictor" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Stall Predictor</a>
        <a href="/fuel-estimator" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Fuel Estimator</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-flame-400 hover:text-flame-300 transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-base-800 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <p class="text-xs text-base-500">
          &copy; 2026 Empirical BBQ · Pitmaster Science &amp; Mathematics Suite
        </p>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-base-600 font-mono">
          Estimates for planning only — always probe to temperature.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  body.page-privacy::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 82% -12%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.14), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(950px 520px at -8% 108%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.09), transparent 55%);
  }
  .policy a {
    color: #fb923c;
  }
  .policy a:hover {
    color: #f97316;
  }
</style>
